author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drywall removal tips…I always use a stud finder when removing drywall. But I also control the depth of cut in case there’s plumbing inside the wall. For example, in this instance the 3” soil stack was right next to the stud. Just something to consider when doing drywall work 🔥#drywall #drywallrepair #bathroomremodel #homerenovations #homerepairtutor
